result.name: business-rates-businesses-with-a-rateable-value-of-less-than-15000
result.notes:
Businesses with a rateable value of less than £12,000 up until Jan 2019, then less than £15,000 thereafter including : Liable Party Name; Property Reference; Rateable Value; Property Address; Property Postcode; Net Debit; Liability Start Date; Relief Indicator and Small Business Rate%

Properties having their charges calculated on the small business multiplier only are also marked SBR. For that reason there are Net Debits for properties with an RV of < £12,000, for example, where the net debit is > £0.00.

For more information on business rates in Calderdale, see the council website: [Business Rates](https://www.calderdale.gov.uk/v2/businesses/business-rates/) .
